                  ARP-SH1 GENERAL COMMANDS MANUAL

NAME
    ls - list directory contents

SYNOPSIS
    ls
    ls [directory]
    ls .
    ls ..

DESCRIPTION
    The `ls` command allows you to list the files and directories
    in the curernt working directory, or in an arbitrary directory
    based on the arguemnt given.

SEE ALSO
    cd, mkdir, mv, rm, touch